            <div class="title">
                Steel Industry And Road Haulage
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1951-11-12/debates/ce07c648-5dbe-4df3-a37f-020fdf6bf96d/HousingHornchurch" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
