<p class="">It seems that the previous Colonial Secretary will be put up to speak about it today. It also seems to me that it is for the Government to decide who shall speak for them in this debate.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-9db28930-e832-4eb8-9026-01f4754f520c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
