        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c246e151-104d-4c92-93f3-f0df05328de0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
