        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-e4e258a4-e9f7-4791-91c6-251791db111e">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-e4e258a4-e9f7-4791-91c6-251791db111e">
                Mr. Wilson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e4e258a4-e9f7-4791-91c6-251791db111e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-11-12/debates/80905b15-d8fc-45dd-9dbe-15b950ba86ab/SteelIndustryAndRoadHaulage#contribution-e4e258a4-e9f7-4791-91c6-251791db111e">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I have not got the figures before me, but I would point out that part of the section that had been nationalised has not been paid for to this day. I have two long-distance road hauliers in my division, neither of whom has been paid in full by the last Government.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-e4e258a4-e9f7-4791-91c6-251791db111e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
