<p class="">Will the hon. Gentleman quote my words?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-3de01dfb-a6e4-4b38-8980-d13804fece99" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
