<p class="">Do I understand that that is during the period of the standstill arrangement suggested?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7ccc4b4f-dedd-453d-b92a-3eb805f63092" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
