<p class="">Perhaps the hon. Member for Wellingborough (Mr. Lindgren), will give me this point, if he will not give me the first—the opportunity for the industry of doing its best for our country. Those are the objectives of our different actions.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
