            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f8fa294c-a37f-4f8a-b7b9-098333440048" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
