<p class="">I am glad that the hon. Member and I agree to that extent and both feel that something more positive should be said about road and rail, but will he go on to say why there was the hurry to introduce this particular piece of legislation and to make these particular proposals when they are not related to the wider issue?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
