        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-52d3334b-dfb4-4d95-9390-9499bbacdd01">
                Mr. Michael Stewart  (Fulham, East)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-52d3334b-dfb4-4d95-9390-9499bbacdd01" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-11-12/debates/80905b15-d8fc-45dd-9dbe-15b950ba86ab/SteelIndustryAndRoadHaulage#contribution-52d3334b-dfb4-4d95-9390-9499bbacdd01">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">If I understood the hon. Gentleman correctly, he said that the Bill to nationalise the industry was rushed through the <span id="752" class="column-number" data-column-number="752"></span> House and Committee. Are we to understand that if any Bill is introduced to de-nationalise the industry he would consider it right that it should take a longer time to go through the House and Committee than the Bill to nationalise it?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-52d3334b-dfb4-4d95-9390-9499bbacdd01" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-11-12/debates/80905b15-d8fc-45dd-9dbe-15b950ba86ab/SteelIndustryAndRoadHaulage#contribution-52d3334b-dfb4-4d95-9390-9499bbacdd01">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
