<p class="">I was referring to the Labour candidates in the City.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-39118e38-9d9b-44d1-84ad-3a70b6586990" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
